WARNING: 
Always make a backup.
Be very careful when updating app/Config directory files.
Take very special attention to core.php and core_phapp.php , do not update salt and cipherSeed.
Take very special attention to database.php, email.php, bootstrap_phapp.php and email_notifications.php files, they have your settings.
Take very special attention to database schema, also look at app/Config/Schema for schema updates.
pHAlkaline strongly suggest the use of a diff software, like winmerge , melddiff or similar to see code and db schema changes.
Clear cache , delete all files at app/tmp/cache subdirectories except empty file
